<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kuo a Lalpa lam pang?
 Kuon Lalna sem ding?
 Mi dang hukdam dingin,
 Kuo a panpih ding?
 Khawvel nawpna nusien,
 Kuoa galdo ding?
 Kuo a Lalpa lam pang?
 Amah di'n kuon ding?
 Zainem in nei sama,
 Nei lungsiet ziekin.

[V2]
 Lalpa di'n ka pang ui,
 Nanga ka hiu ui.

[V3]
 2. Lopina chawihatna,
 Mai lungtup lo in;
 Sepaih In I pang ui,
 Zawhna La sa di'n;
 Mite hinna dinga,
 A thih tak ziekin;
 Isu min samta chuh,
 A lam pang hin au,
 Na hehpihnan ei sawl,
 Nei lungsiet ziekin.

[V4]
 3. Isu, Nang in nei chawi,
 Sana leh sum lo'n;
 Na hinna thisan in,
 Nang hun chawian di'n;
 Na kawma hung cheng chuh,
 Vangsakna'n na thuom;
 Nang nei suthalawp a,
 Nei suohchak sak tai;
 Nei tatna lopi leh,
 Nei lungsiet ziekin.

[V5]
 4. Kidona lauhum in,
 Melma hat mahleh;
 Lalpen sepaihte chuh,
 Kuoman zo puona;
 A puonlap nuoi achun,
 Gal zo ngeingei ding;
 A thu zuou ngeilo chun,
 Zawhna thu ei tiem;
 Lawp takin ka pang ui,
 Nei lungsiet ziekin.</lyrics>
<title>WHO IS ON THE LORD'S SIDE?</title>
<hymn_number>308</hymn_number>
</song>